column5: Well, I didn't quite live up to my last day on the water but landing two more for a second straight trip was nice.  I was trying a new section of the Ottawa, almost 30km from where I got the others ones this week and it paid off.   Nothing too huge but I figure landing a 38" and a 32" in the same spot shows promise.  Needless to say, it'll be getting a little bit more attention next week.      Cheers,  MW
lookin forward to seeing these pics!  haha.
